# Classgrid — All Overview Wireframe Layouts

> **Style:** Agora Console — clean, sharp, square corners, no heavy rounded
> **Sidebar:** 240px, `#111827` bg | **Content:** `#000000` bg | **Accent:** `#34d399`

---

## 1. 🔥 SUPER ADMIN Overview

**Who:** Platform owner (you). Manages ALL organizations.
**Desktop only.** No mobile needed.

### Left Sidebar
```
┌──────────────────────────────┐
│  ⚡ Classgrid                │  Logo + wordmark
│     Super Admin              │  Subtitle
│                              │
│  ─ OVERVIEW ─────────────── │
│  📊 Overview                │  /superadmin/dashboard
│  📈 Analytics                │  /superadmin/analytics
│  🔔 Alerts                  │  /superadmin/alerts
│                              │
│  ─ ORGANIZATIONS ─────────  │
