| Overview | Route Prefix | Sidebar Width | Desktop | Mobile |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Super Admin** | `/superadmin/*` | 240px | ✅ | ❌ |
| **Org Admin** | `/org/*` | 240px | ✅ | ❌ |
| **Admission Dept** | `/dept/admissions/*` | 240px | ✅ | ❌ |
