| **HR & Payroll** | `/dept/hr/*` | 240px | ✅ | ❌ |
| **Hostel/Transport** | `/dept/hostel/*` | 240px | ✅ | ❌ |
| **Faculty** | `/*` (existing) | 240px | ✅ | ✅ App |
| **Student** | `/*` (existing) | 240px | ✅ | ✅ App |

