## Sidebar Component Architecture

**One reusable `<OverviewSidebar>` component** that takes a config prop:

```jsx
<OverviewSidebar
  logo="Classgrid"
  subtitle="Admission Dept"
  sections={[
    { label: 'ADMISSIONS', items: [...] },
    { label: 'CONFIGURATION', items: [...] },
    { label: 'REPORTS', items: [...] },
  ]}
  user={{ name: 'John', email: 'john@test.edu' }}
/>
```

Each dashboard page just provides its own sidebar config — **one component, many views**.
